name: Lease Negotiation AI Assistant
content:
Lease Negotiation AI Project

Automated analysis of Verizon lease agreements for optimal contract renewals


Project Overview


Objective:

Develop an AI system that -

  • Analyzes Verizon commercial lease agreements
  • Identifies cost-saving opportunities
  • Generates data-driven negotiation strategies


Key Features:

  • Lease Extraction :: Parses rent, terms, and clauses from PDFs
  • Market Comparison :: Benchmarks against competitor rates
  • Performance Integration :: Considers foot traffic/revenue data
  • Risk Scoring :: Rates negotiation points 1-5 (low-high risk)


Components:

Input Handler

  • Accepts: PDF leases, Market Data., Performance Metrics
  • Validates file formats and completeness

AI Processing Layer

  • LLM: GPT-4 with custom prompt engineering
  • Chunking: Page segments with metadata tagging

Output Generator

  • Formats: Reports, Email templates


Output

Recommendation Summary

Recommendation Insights
description: Automated analysis of Verizon lease agreements for optimal contract renewals
